## What is TalentTrack?

A full-stack student skill tracking and ranking platform with:
- ✅ **THREE separate dashboards** (Student, College, Admin)
- ✅ **ONE shared backend** (Node.js + Express + MongoDB)
- ✅ **Left sidebar navigation** with 5 pages
- ✅ **4 ranking cards** on home page
- ✅ **4 coding platform cards** in portfolio
- ✅ **Global and college leaderboards**
- ✅ **Engineer score calculation**

## Get Started in 5 Minutes

```bash
# 1. Start Backend
cd backend
npm install
# Create .env file (see .env.example)
npm run dev

# 2. Start Student Dashboard (new terminal)
cd student-dashboard
npm install
npm start
```

Open http://localhost:3000 and register!

## Project Structure

```
TalentTrack/
├── backend/              # Express.js API
├── student-dashboard/    # React app (main)
├── college-dashboard/    # React app (college admin)
├── admin-dashboard/      # React app (super admin)
└── docs/                 # Documentation files
```

